<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1192] Enable DumpLogSegments tool to deserialize messages</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1192</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the DumpLogSegments tool reads the message payloads as strings by default, which will not display the messages correctly if the messages are deserialized with another class. By enablding deserialization with a customized class we can use this tool to debug more issues where I need to read the message content.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12686328">KAFKA-1192</key>
            <summary>Enable DumpLogSegments tool to deserialize messages</summary>
