                            <comment id="14067444" author="omkreddy" created="Sat, 19 Jul 2014 08:31:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Introduced new command-line parameter &quot;decoder-class&quot; to pass customized Decoder class.  This class should implement kafka.serializer.Decoder trait.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14068611" author="omkreddy" created="Mon, 21 Jul 2014 15:17:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated reviewboard &lt;a href=&quot;https://reviews.apache.org/r/23705/diff/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://reviews.apache.org/r/23705/diff/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
